{"tid":325354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉於航機上踢傷空姐 支那女今獲准保釋","createTime":"2017-07-17T07:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T07:08:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29ae0e777b0789234192c37f1f10a1def35129ac","tid":325354,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170717/large/1500271076_0a45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170717%2Flarge%2F1500271076_0a45.jpg&h=5a21c8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170717/56966221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170717%2F56966221&d=II5Klk0GI3zo1%2FaEkuCQgv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7aca6544\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170717%2F56966221&h=77dc9c74\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170717/56966221</a><br />\n<br />\n 支那女乘客上周五乘坐國泰航機由曼谷回港，其間疑因收拾餐盤問題與一名空姐發生爭執，空姐被人推撞及踢傷左腳。女乘客抵港後被控普通襲擊罪，日前提堂後還柙監房，今申請保釋獲批准，獲准以3,000元現金擔保，期間不准離港。<br />\n<br />\n被告劉曉曉（34歲），她被指於本月14日在一班由曼谷來港的航機內襲擊女子阮亦雯（29歲）。被告暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至8月28日，待控方進一步調查及索取法律意見。"},{"pid":"75bc5fda35f537d6a99e332d4bc9830a649553aa","tid":325354,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"支那賤畜應該永遠禁飛"}]}